"изтичането на този ПЕРИОД.\n"

#: src/timeout.c:279
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"  -f, --foreground\n"
"         when not running timeout directly from a shell prompt,\n"
"         allow COMMAND to read from the TTY and get TTY signals;\n"
"         in this mode, children of COMMAND will not be timed out\n"
msgstr ""
